Ross Patterson, Jessie Wiseman and Dan Hollaway bring you the realest fake news of the week with Trump’s new coronavirus projections, predict how people are going to vote in November with possible Coronavirus restrictions, discuss Doc Antle speaking out against the “Tiger King” documentary series, cover the King of Thailand living the rest of his days in a Bavarian hotel with a bunch of women, talk about evidence of rainforests in Antarctica, and end the show with analyzing major news channels’ numbers.
